    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1900-09-18T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1900-09-18T00:00:00-05:00" n="521"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d521">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Wu</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hill</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Chinese Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1900-09-18">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 18, 1900</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have honor, on behalf of the Imperial
                    Government and people of China, to express to you, and through you to the
                    Government and people of the United States, their deep sympathy occasioned by
                    the dire calamity that has recently befallen the city of Galveston, Texas. To
                    this expression of sympathy I beg to add that of my own.</p>
                <p>I avail, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Wu Ting-fang.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
